This paper deals with face recognition using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of adversarial losses and deep neural networks, which are common in machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of image inpainting and pose correction, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR).
